<div id="review_1133885603" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1133885603" />
    <a title="Rubina" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7326446-rubina"><img alt="Rubina" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1516674270p2/7326446.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1133885603?book_show_action=true">Dec 16, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rubina" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rubina" href="/user/show/7326446-rubina">Rubina</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=mindfulness">mindfulness</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=psychology">psychology</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=philosophy">philosophy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=must-read">must-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=personal-development">personal-development</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=spiritual">spiritual</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7326446-rubina?shelf=neuroscience">neuroscience</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1133885603" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14592453063915147226">This has to be one of my favourite books on happiness and positive psychology. Covering such concepts as seeking happiness within/without, the alchemy of suffering, egoism, managing our thoughts and disturbing emotions, compassion, altrusium, happiness set point and the impact positive thinking and mediation has on the neuroplasticity, Ricard&apos;s coverage of the topic is comprehensive without being too heavy or technical. <br/>Being happy is a skill which can only be acquired through practice, and this</span>
  <span id="freeText14592453063915147226" style="display:none">This has to be one of my favourite books on happiness and positive psychology. Covering such concepts as seeking happiness within/without, the alchemy of suffering, egoism, managing our thoughts and disturbing emotions, compassion, altrusium, happiness set point and the impact positive thinking and mediation has on the neuroplasticity, Ricard's coverage of the topic is comprehensive without being too heavy or technical. <br />Being happy is a skill which can only be acquired through practice, and this book is an excellent guide.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14592453063915147226" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


