<div id="review_661424512" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/661424512" />
    <a title="Max" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3642433-max"><img alt="Max" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1462626470p2/3642433.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/661424512?book_show_action=true">Jul 07, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Max" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Max" href="/user/show/3642433-max">Max</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=did-not-finish">did-not-finish</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=religion">religion</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=science">science</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=50-book-pledge-2013">50-book-pledge-2013</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=zen">zen</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=philosophy">philosophy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=buddhism">buddhism</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=library">library</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642433-max?shelf=spirituality">spirituality</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer661424512" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13236985508983579864">An interesting philosophical and scientific look at Happiness within life and Buddhism.<br/>A bit hard to get through, but an interesting read nonetheless. I think that because of the author&apos;s scientific background, as well as the fact this book is translated from his original French makes it a harder read than other books on this topic. Not one I would recommend as a start into this topic, but one that should make it onto your to-read lists if this is a topic you&apos;ve already started reading about.</span>
  <span id="freeText13236985508983579864" style="display:none">An interesting philosophical and scientific look at Happiness within life and Buddhism.<br />A bit hard to get through, but an interesting read nonetheless. I think that because of the author's scientific background, as well as the fact this book is translated from his original French makes it a harder read than other books on this topic. Not one I would recommend as a start into this topic, but one that should make it onto your to-read lists if this is a topic you've already started reading about.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13236985508983579864" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


